    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296320/extras/c647b8e4b1311c2285a6025dd18ab366.poster.avif?t=1729854249\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296320/extras/c647b8e4b1311c2285a6025dd18ab366.webm?t=1729854249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296320/extras/c647b8e4b1311c2285a6025dd18ab366.mp4?t=1729854249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The player starts in a helicopter and is dropped into no man’s land with only one weapon to defend themselves against what's lurking in the shadows. They must kill zombies for points progressing round to round while upgrading their weapon with attachments, completing tasks, and fighting off bosses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296320/extras/3ac86576ddf211e3a9214a567c335d16.poster.avif?t=1729854249\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296320/extras/3ac86576ddf211e3a9214a567c335d16.webm?t=1729854249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296320/extras/3ac86576ddf211e3a9214a567c335d16.mp4?t=1729854249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296320/extras/3801e650279ae26272f452f29b16cfb6.poster.avif?t=1729854249\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296320/extras/3801e650279ae26272f452f29b16cfb6.webm?t=1729854249\" type=\"video/webm; codec